step_data.thought:
Looking at the current page, I notice we're now on the Customers / Customers page in the Magento Admin panel. The page shows a message "You saved the customer." which indicates that our customer registration with tax/VAT information was successful. The customer list appears to be empty or not showing any records at the moment ("0 records found"), but the success message confirms that our action was completed successfully.

To summarize what we accomplished:
1. We created a new customer (John Doe) with email john.doe.business23@example.com
2. We added the Tax/VAT Number GB123456789 for business purchases
3. We successfully saved the customer

Since we've completed the requested task of registering a new customer with tax/VAT information for business purchases, I should inform the user that the task has been completed successfully.
